IP Classification
================================================================================

This project contains implementations organized into the following tiers:

Tier 1 — Original Innovations (proprietary to CARF/CYNEPIC):
  - Entropy-aware Cynefin routing logic
  - Deterministic Guardian enforcement architecture
  - EpistemicState provenance schema
  - Complexity-adaptive decision pipeline (router → engine → guardian → graph)

Tier 2 — Proprietary Orchestration (novel compositions of known methods):
  - Causal inference pipeline integration (DAG → identify → estimate → refute)
  - Bayesian belief tracking with tool reliability monitoring
  - Policy chain evaluation with circuit breaker and loop detection
  - Risk-aware policy evaluation combining Bayesian scores and governance

Tier 3 — Supporting Infrastructure (standard patterns, project-specific):
  - Append-only audit trail
  - Budget-aware routing
  - Workflow graph orchestration
  - HITL escalation lifecycle

Tier 4 — Third-Party (no IP claim):
  - petgraph (graph algorithms)
  - ndarray (numerical arrays)
  - statrs (statistical distributions)
  - regorus (Rego policy evaluation)
  - serde (serialization)
  - tokio (async runtime)

Trade secrets explicitly NOT included in this repository:
  - Specific threshold calibrations and scoring weights
  - Trained model artifacts
  - Policy enforcement matrices
  - Production deployment configurations

