Framework Attribution
================================================================================

cynepic-rs implements concepts from:

  - The Cynefin framework by Dave Snowden (public domain framework)
  - Pearl's causal inference framework (published academic methodology)
  - The Bayes-Ball algorithm by Shachter (published algorithm)
  - The Metropolis-Hastings algorithm (published statistical method)
  - The circuit breaker pattern by Martin Fowler (published pattern)
